data.title: badge, German, Reichsarbeitstagung Druck und Papier in Leipzig 1938
data.meta_description: Circular compressed paper badge, in a white and gold finish. On the face is a design depicting a coat-of-arms, with three shields, in white on a gold background, with a DAF logo of a swastika within a cogged wheel beneath. There is a border inscription REICHSARBEITSTAGUNG DRUCK UND PAPIER IN LEIPZIG 1938.
